  "text": "Beta-gamma threshold adjustment was generally used when certain classes do not have a sufficient number of training examples, which may lead to poor SVM recall scores [CITATION_1] . It was used by [CITATION_2] to binary classify a set of articles and proved to improve recall with little effect on precision.",
